      <p class="col-lg-10 fs-4" style="text-align: justify;">Fill out this form with your book title, isbn and the rating you think it deserves! </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto col-lg-5">

    <form action="/add" method="post" class="p-4 p-md-5 rounded-3"  style="box-shadow: 10px 10px 5px  #674636; ; border:4px solid#674636; background-color: #fbfbf7;">
